About Dr. Amit Mittal

Dr Amit Mittal is one of the best cardiologists in South Delhi. He is well-known for his expertise in heart disease. As a specialist, Dr Mittal has trained himself in treating chest pain, high blood pressure, irregular heartbeats, shortness of breath, numbness, weakness and coldness in the legs and arms, as well as other heart and vascular problems.

Diseases like heart attacks, congestive heart failure, congenital heart disease and coronary heart disease are the leading causes of death for both men and women around the world. To diagnose a heart condition, cardiologists like Dr Amit may conduct physical exams and order tests such as electrocardiograms (ECGs), blood tests, exercise stress tests, TMT, X-rays and MRI scans. Once they have a diagnosis, they will discuss a treatment plan with you. They may suggest lifestyle changes and prescribe medicine. More serious conditions may require surgery.

A highly skilled and trained expert in cardiology, Dr Mittal has achieved impressive accomplishments and an overwhelming success rate in his field. He performs complex procedures such as angioplasties, angiographies, electrophysical studies, mitral valve repair, and cardiac catheterisation. He also performs pacemaker implantations which are done to treat patients who have very slow or irregular heartbeats. He educates his patients about healthy habits that promote good heart health. 

With 11 years of experience, Dr Amit Mittal is considered one of the best cardiologists in South Delhi. He says, “The greatest gift you can give your family and the world is a healthy you."
